-Each gate produces a PASS / FAIL / N/A verdict. FAILs do **not** block emission — they become inline `⚠️ GAP:` markers + entries in the final `## Unresolved Gaps` table + flip the plan's `**Status**` to `DRAFT — UNRESOLVED GAPS`.
